  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to demonstrate efficacy of SK-1404 against placebo for the
      treatment of subjects with nocturia due to nocturnal polyuria, during 4 weeks of treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
